# CTA-PX Curriculum Scripts (v1)

Short, repeatable visual sequences for kids.

---

## SCRIPT 1 — Confusion → Reset → Understanding
```
O ⟂
O ↓
O ↑
(O→R→S)
```

---

## SCRIPT 2 — Overwhelm → Space → Ready
```
O ↓
O ←
→ O
```

---

## SCRIPT 3 — Conflict → Pause → Try Again → Okay
```
O X
O ↓
O ↑
O_
(O→R→S)
```

---

## SCRIPT 4 — Mixed Up → Clarify → Success
```
O → R ~ S
O ↑
(O→R→S)
```

---

## SCRIPT 5 — Too Fast → Slow → Explain
```
O ↓
O ↑
(O→R→S)
```

---

## SCRIPT 6 — Emotional Freeze → Reset → Help → OK
```
O ↓
↺ O
O X
(O→R→S)
```

---

## SCRIPT 7 — “I’m Not Ready Yet”
```
O ←
```

## …and “I’m Ready Now”
```
→ O
```
